Advantages of Arrays
  a) Whenever the bunch of similar types datas are required to store arrays comes in to pictures.
  b) It can store multiples of values within a single variable.
  c) At array its easy to access the datas.

Dis-Advantages of Arrays
  a) Arrays can't Store diffrent type of datas.(Arrays can store only similar types of datas)
  b) Its must needs the contigueus memory allocations.
  c) The size of the array can't be change after creation.
